    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the Slums of New Mumbai!</strong></h2>Divided Skies is a single player flight adventure game where you play as Kyra, a member of the Nandaka gang, as she completes dangerous missions transporting illegal tech and mechanical enhancements while fighting off rival gangs. Shoot enemies, chase down foes, and explore hidden areas as you uncover the secrets of the metropolis called New Mumbai taking place in the year 2100<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Satistying VTOL flight movement</strong>: Experience the thrill of fast and easy-to-control VTOL flight movement as you speed through the vibrant slums of New Mumbai on Kyra's Hoverbike.<br></li><li><strong>Clear missions and progress the story</strong>: As you play the game your main objective will be to clear various objectives to progress through the story uncovering more secrets of New Mumbai and Kyra!<br></li><li><strong>Engaging combat encounters</strong>: Take down enemies in your way as you progress through the story, with exciting and varied combat encounters that challenge your skills as Kyra.<br></li><li><strong>Open to explore environment</strong>: Explore the vibrant and sprawling slums of New Mumbai at your leisure, with a beautifully crafted open-world environment<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic traffic</strong>: Experience dynamic traffic as you fly through the slums, being careful not to harm innocent civilians.</li></ul>",
